data.title: Classic Rock 105.1 – Acadiana's Classic Rock – Lafayette Classic Rock Radio
data.meta_description: Classic Rock 105.1, KFTE-FM Radio,  a Townsquare Media station, plays the best classic rock music in Lafayette, Louisiana.
